Invocation Name: cat summon
Developer Terms of Use
des:
A collection of common sound effects that can trigger your cat to come to your Alexa device. 

Over usage without actually providing snacks to your cat(s) may reduce the effectiveness of these sound effects. 

Current Available Sounds
- Snack Bag
- Snack Box

Developer Privacy Policy
